  user_input {
    user_response: "Apply the \"Sleek Interface\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Sleek Interface\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"flex flex-col h-screen w-full bg-[#0A0F1E] text-slate-200 font-sans p-6 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n  <!-- Header Navigation -->\\n  <header class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between mb-6 shrink-0\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-[#38BDF8] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\\\">\\n        <svg class=\\\"w-6 h-6 text-[#0A0F1E]\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M3 15a4 4 0 004 4h9a5 5 0 10-.1-9.999 5.002 5.002 0 10-9.78 2.096A4.001 4.001 0 003 15z\\\"/></svg>\\n      </div>\\n      <div>\\n        <h1 class=\\\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white\\\">SkyClear <span class=\\\"text-[#38BDF8] font-light\\\">Briefing</span></h1>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500\\\">Aviation Weather Decoder</p>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4 bg-[#1E293B] p-1.5 rounded-xl border border-slate-700/50\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center px-3\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-xs font-mono text-slate-500 mr-2\\\">ICAO:</span>\\n        <input type=\\\"text\\\" value=\\\"KJFK\\\" class=\\\"bg-transparent text-white font-bold uppercase w-16 focus:outline-none\\\" readonly />\\n      </div>\\n      <button class=\\\"bg-[#38BDF8] hover:bg-sky-400 text-[#0A0F1E] font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm transition-colors\\\">\\n        New Briefing\\n      </button>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"text-right\\\">\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500 uppercase font-semibold\\\">Last Fetch</p>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-300\\\">15:51 UTC (2 mins ago)</p>\\n      </div>\\n      <button class=\\\"p-2 hover:bg-slate-800 rounded-full transition-colors\\\">\\n        <svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5 text-slate-400\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15\\\"/></svg>\\n      </button>\\n    </div>\\n  </header>\\n\\n  <main class=\\\"grid grid-cols-12 gap-6 flex-1 min-h-0\\\">\\n    <!-- Left Section: METAR Decoder -->\\n    <div class=\\\"col-span-8 flex flex-col gap-6\\\">\\n      <!-- Raw METAR Section -->\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-4\\\">\\n        <label class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 font-bold mb-2 block\\\">Raw METAR</label>\\n        <code class=\\\"text-[#38BDF8] font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed block break-all\\\">\\n          KJFK 241551Z 29015G22KT 10SM FEW040 SCT250 18/08 A3002 RMK AO2 SLP165 T01830083\\n        </code>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Briefing Summary -->\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-sky-900/10 border-l-4 border-[#38BDF8] p-5 rounded-r-2xl\\\">\\n        <h3 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-[#38BDF8] uppercase mb-1 tracking-wide\\\">Plain English Summary</h3>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-slate-300 leading-relaxed\\\">\\n          Winds are moderate from the West-Northwest at 15 knots, gusting to 22. Visibility is excellent at 10 miles. A few clouds observed at 4,000 feet. Temperature is 18\302\260C with a 10\302\260 spread. Conditions are <span class=\\\"text-[#22C55E] font-bold\\\">VFR</span> \342\200\224 suitable for visual flight operations at John F. Kennedy Intl.\\n        </p>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Detailed Metrics Grid -->\\n      <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 flex-1 overflow-y-auto pr-2\\\">\\n        <!-- Station & Time -->\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-[#1E293B] border border-slate-700/50 p-4 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase text-slate-500 font-bold\\\">Station & Time</span>\\n          <div class=\\\"mt-2\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-white\\\">KJFK</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1\\\">24 Oct, 11:51 Local</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400\\\">15:51 UTC</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Wind -->\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-[#1E293B] border border-slate-700/50 p-4 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between border-l-4 border-l-[#22C55E]\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase text-slate-500 font-bold\\\">Wind</span>\\n          <div class=\\\"mt-2\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-white\\\">290\302\260 @ 15<span class=\\\"text-sm font-normal text-slate-400 ml-1 italic\\\">G22KT</span></p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1 uppercase tracking-tight\\\">WNW &mdash; Moderate Breeze</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Visibility -->\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-[#1E293B] border border-slate-700/50 p-4 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between border-l-4 border-l-[#22C55E]\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase text-slate-500 font-bold\\\">Visibility</span>\\n          <div class=\\\"mt-2\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-white\\\">10+ SM</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xs text-[#22C55E] mt-1 font-semibold uppercase\\\">Excellent (P6SM)</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Clouds -->\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-[#1E293B] border border-slate-700/50 p-4 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase text-slate-500 font-bold\\\">Cloud Layers</span>\\n          <div class=\\\"mt-2 flex flex-col gap-1\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-sm text-slate-200\\\"><span class=\\\"font-mono text-[#38BDF8]\\\">FEW</span> 4,000\' AGL</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-sm text-slate-400\\\"><span class=\\\"font-mono text-slate-500\\\">SCT</span> 25,000\' AGL</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Temp & Dew -->\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-[#1E293B] border border-slate-700/50 p-4 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase text-slate-500 font-bold\\\">Temp & Dewpoint</span>\\n          <div class=\\\"mt-2\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xl font-bold text-white\\\">18\302\260C / 08\302\260C</p>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 mt-1\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-slate-800 rounded border border-slate-700\\\">Spread: 10\302\260C</span>\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#22C55E] font-bold uppercase\\\">Low Fog Risk</span>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Pressure -->\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-[#1E293B] border border-slate-700/50 p-4 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase text-slate-500 font-bold\\\">Pressure (QNH)</span>\\n          <div class=\\\"mt-2\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-white\\\">30.02 <span class=\\\"text-sm font-normal text-slate-400\\\">inHg</span></p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1 font-mono\\\">1016.6 hPa</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Right Section: Category & Forecast -->\\n    <div class=\\\"col-span-4 flex flex-col gap-6\\\">\\n      <!-- Flight Category Card -->\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-[#22C55E]/10 border-2 border-[#22C55E] rounded-3xl p-6 text-center\\\">\\n        <h2 class=\\\"text-5xl font-black text-[#22C55E] tracking-tighter mb-1\\\">VFR</h2>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-white font-bold\\\">Visual Flight Rules</p>\\n        <div class=\\\"mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-[#22C55E]/20\\\">\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-[#22C55E] leading-snug uppercase tracking-wider\\\">\\n            Ceiling > 3,000ft &amp; Vis > 5SM<br/>Safe for primary student solo ops\\n          </p>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- TAF Preview -->\\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-slate-900/30 border border-slate-800 rounded-3xl p-5 flex flex-col\\\">\\n        <h3 class=\\\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500 font-bold mb-4\\\">Forecast (TAF) Timeline</h3>\\n        \\n        <div class=\\\"space-y-3 flex-1 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n          <!-- TAF Card 1 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-[#1E293B] rounded-xl p-3 border-l-4 border-l-[#22C55E]\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#38BDF8]\\\">FROM 18:00Z</span>\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-[#22C55E] px-1 bg-[#22C55E]/10 rounded\\\">VFR</span>\\n            </div>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-200 mt-1\\\">Wind shifting 31012KT. Scattered clouds at 5,000ft.</p>\\n          </div>\\n          \\n          <!-- TAF Card 2 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-[#1E293B] rounded-xl p-3 border-l-4 border-l-[#38BDF8]\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#38BDF8]\\\">BECMG 22:00Z</span>\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-[#38BDF8] px-1 bg-[#38BDF8]/10 rounded\\\">MVFR</span>\\n            </div>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-200 mt-1\\\">Visibility dropping to 4SM in mist. Broken layer at 2,500ft.</p>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <!-- TAF Card 3 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-[#1E293B] rounded-xl p-3 border-l-4 border-l-[#F59E0B]\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#38BDF8]\\\">TEMPO 02:00Z</span>\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-[#F59E0B] px-1 bg-[#F59E0B]/10 rounded\\\">IFR</span>\\n            </div>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-200 mt-1 text-slate-400\\\">Reduced visibility 2SM in light rain showers. Fog potential.</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Pilot Notes Panel -->\\n        <div class=\\\"mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-slate-800\\\">\\n          <h4 class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase font-bold text-slate-500 mb-2\\\">Pilot Notes</h4>\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-[#0A0F1E] rounded-lg p-3 text-[11px] text-slate-400 italic\\\">\\n            Current dewpoint spread (10\302\260C) is healthy. Monitor for radiation fog if temperature drops below 11\302\260C tonight.\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </main>\\n\\n  <!-- Sticky Footer -->\\n  <footer class=\\\"mt-6 flex justify-between items-center text-[11px] text-slate-500 shrink-0 border-t border-slate-800/50 pt-4\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex gap-4\\\">\\n      <span>VFR MINIMUMS: 3SM / 1000\' AGL</span>\\n      <span class=\\\"text-slate-700\\\">|</span>\\n      <span>SOURCE: NOAA AVIATION WEATHER CENTER</span>\\n    </div>\\n    <p>Built for Student Pilots by <span class=\\\"text-[#38BDF8]\\\">SkyClear Engineering</span> &mdash; Purdue Aerospace Portfolio</p>\\n  </footer>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"Sleek Interface\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Sleek Interface\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"flex flex-col h-screen w-full bg-[#0A0F1E] text-slate-200 font-sans p-6 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n  <!-- Header Navigation -->\\n  <header class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between mb-6 shrink-0\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-10 h-10 bg-[#38BDF8] rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\\\">\\n        <svg class=\\\"w-6 h-6 text-[#0A0F1E]\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M3 15a4 4 0 004 4h9a5 5 0 10-.1-9.999 5.002 5.002 0 10-9.78 2.096A4.001 4.001 0 003 15z\\\"/></svg>\\n      </div>\\n      <div>\\n        <h1 class=\\\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white\\\">SkyClear <span class=\\\"text-[#38BDF8] font-light\\\">Briefing</span></h1>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500\\\">Aviation Weather Decoder</p>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4 bg-[#1E293B] p-1.5 rounded-xl border border-slate-700/50\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center px-3\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-xs font-mono text-slate-500 mr-2\\\">ICAO:</span>\\n        <input type=\\\"text\\\" value=\\\"KJFK\\\" class=\\\"bg-transparent text-white font-bold uppercase w-16 focus:outline-none\\\" readonly />\\n      </div>\\n      <button class=\\\"bg-[#38BDF8] hover:bg-sky-400 text-[#0A0F1E] font-bold px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-sm transition-colors\\\">\\n        New Briefing\\n      </button>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"text-right\\\">\\n        <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-500 uppercase font-semibold\\\">Last Fetch</p>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-300\\\">15:51 UTC (2 mins ago)</p>\\n      </div>\\n      <button class=\\\"p-2 hover:bg-slate-800 rounded-full transition-colors\\\">\\n        <svg class=\\\"w-5 h-5 text-slate-400\\\" fill=\\\"none\\\" stroke=\\\"currentColor\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path stroke-linecap=\\\"round\\\" stroke-linejoin=\\\"round\\\" stroke-width=\\\"2\\\" d=\\\"M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15\\\"/></svg>\\n      </button>\\n    </div>\\n  </header>\\n\\n  <main class=\\\"grid grid-cols-12 gap-6 flex-1 min-h-0\\\">\\n    <!-- Left Section: METAR Decoder -->\\n    <div class=\\\"col-span-8 flex flex-col gap-6\\\">\\n      <!-- Raw METAR Section -->\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-4\\\">\\n        <label class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 font-bold mb-2 block\\\">Raw METAR</label>\\n        <code class=\\\"text-[#38BDF8] font-mono text-sm leading-relaxed block break-all\\\">\\n          KJFK 241551Z 29015G22KT 10SM FEW040 SCT250 18/08 A3002 RMK AO2 SLP165 T01830083\\n        </code>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Briefing Summary -->\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-sky-900/10 border-l-4 border-[#38BDF8] p-5 rounded-r-2xl\\\">\\n        <h3 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-[#38BDF8] uppercase mb-1 tracking-wide\\\">Plain English Summary</h3>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-slate-300 leading-relaxed\\\">\\n          Winds are moderate from the West-Northwest at 15 knots, gusting to 22. Visibility is excellent at 10 miles. A few clouds observed at 4,000 feet. Temperature is 18\302\260C with a 10\302\260 spread. Conditions are <span class=\\\"text-[#22C55E] font-bold\\\">VFR</span> \342\200\224 suitable for visual flight operations at John F. Kennedy Intl.\\n        </p>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Detailed Metrics Grid -->\\n      <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 flex-1 overflow-y-auto pr-2\\\">\\n        <!-- Station & Time -->\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-[#1E293B] border border-slate-700/50 p-4 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase text-slate-500 font-bold\\\">Station & Time</span>\\n          <div class=\\\"mt-2\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-white\\\">KJFK</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1\\\">24 Oct, 11:51 Local</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400\\\">15:51 UTC</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Wind -->\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-[#1E293B] border border-slate-700/50 p-4 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between border-l-4 border-l-[#22C55E]\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase text-slate-500 font-bold\\\">Wind</span>\\n          <div class=\\\"mt-2\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-white\\\">290\302\260 @ 15<span class=\\\"text-sm font-normal text-slate-400 ml-1 italic\\\">G22KT</span></p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1 uppercase tracking-tight\\\">WNW &mdash; Moderate Breeze</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Visibility -->\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-[#1E293B] border border-slate-700/50 p-4 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between border-l-4 border-l-[#22C55E]\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase text-slate-500 font-bold\\\">Visibility</span>\\n          <div class=\\\"mt-2\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-white\\\">10+ SM</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xs text-[#22C55E] mt-1 font-semibold uppercase\\\">Excellent (P6SM)</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Clouds -->\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-[#1E293B] border border-slate-700/50 p-4 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase text-slate-500 font-bold\\\">Cloud Layers</span>\\n          <div class=\\\"mt-2 flex flex-col gap-1\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-sm text-slate-200\\\"><span class=\\\"font-mono text-[#38BDF8]\\\">FEW</span> 4,000\' AGL</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-sm text-slate-400\\\"><span class=\\\"font-mono text-slate-500\\\">SCT</span> 25,000\' AGL</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Temp & Dew -->\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-[#1E293B] border border-slate-700/50 p-4 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase text-slate-500 font-bold\\\">Temp & Dewpoint</span>\\n          <div class=\\\"mt-2\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xl font-bold text-white\\\">18\302\260C / 08\302\260C</p>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 mt-1\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] px-1.5 py-0.5 bg-slate-800 rounded border border-slate-700\\\">Spread: 10\302\260C</span>\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#22C55E] font-bold uppercase\\\">Low Fog Risk</span>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Pressure -->\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-[#1E293B] border border-slate-700/50 p-4 rounded-2xl flex flex-col justify-between\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase text-slate-500 font-bold\\\">Pressure (QNH)</span>\\n          <div class=\\\"mt-2\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-2xl font-bold text-white\\\">30.02 <span class=\\\"text-sm font-normal text-slate-400\\\">inHg</span></p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400 mt-1 font-mono\\\">1016.6 hPa</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Right Section: Category & Forecast -->\\n    <div class=\\\"col-span-4 flex flex-col gap-6\\\">\\n      <!-- Flight Category Card -->\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-[#22C55E]/10 border-2 border-[#22C55E] rounded-3xl p-6 text-center\\\">\\n        <h2 class=\\\"text-5xl font-black text-[#22C55E] tracking-tighter mb-1\\\">VFR</h2>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-white font-bold\\\">Visual Flight Rules</p>\\n        <div class=\\\"mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-[#22C55E]/20\\\">\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-[#22C55E] leading-snug uppercase tracking-wider\\\">\\n            Ceiling > 3,000ft &amp; Vis > 5SM<br/>Safe for primary student solo ops\\n          </p>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- TAF Preview -->\\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-slate-900/30 border border-slate-800 rounded-3xl p-5 flex flex-col\\\">\\n        <h3 class=\\\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-500 font-bold mb-4\\\">Forecast (TAF) Timeline</h3>\\n        \\n        <div class=\\\"space-y-3 flex-1 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n          <!-- TAF Card 1 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-[#1E293B] rounded-xl p-3 border-l-4 border-l-[#22C55E]\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#38BDF8]\\\">FROM 18:00Z</span>\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-[#22C55E] px-1 bg-[#22C55E]/10 rounded\\\">VFR</span>\\n            </div>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-200 mt-1\\\">Wind shifting 31012KT. Scattered clouds at 5,000ft.</p>\\n          </div>\\n          \\n          <!-- TAF Card 2 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-[#1E293B] rounded-xl p-3 border-l-4 border-l-[#38BDF8]\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#38BDF8]\\\">BECMG 22:00Z</span>\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-[#38BDF8] px-1 bg-[#38BDF8]/10 rounded\\\">MVFR</span>\\n            </div>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-200 mt-1\\\">Visibility dropping to 4SM in mist. Broken layer at 2,500ft.</p>\\n          </div>\\n\\n          <!-- TAF Card 3 -->\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-[#1E293B] rounded-xl p-3 border-l-4 border-l-[#F59E0B]\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#38BDF8]\\\">TEMPO 02:00Z</span>\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-bold text-[#F59E0B] px-1 bg-[#F59E0B]/10 rounded\\\">IFR</span>\\n            </div>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-200 mt-1 text-slate-400\\\">Reduced visibility 2SM in light rain showers. Fog potential.</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <!-- Pilot Notes Panel -->\\n        <div class=\\\"mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-slate-800\\\">\\n          <h4 class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase font-bold text-slate-500 mb-2\\\">Pilot Notes</h4>\\n          <div class=\\\"bg-[#0A0F1E] rounded-lg p-3 text-[11px] text-slate-400 italic\\\">\\n            Current dewpoint spread (10\302\260C) is healthy. Monitor for radiation fog if temperature drops below 11\302\260C tonight.\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </main>\\n\\n  <!-- Sticky Footer -->\\n  <footer class=\\\"mt-6 flex justify-between items-center text-[11px] text-slate-500 shrink-0 border-t border-slate-800/50 pt-4\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex gap-4\\\">\\n      <span>VFR MINIMUMS: 3SM / 1000\' AGL</span>\\n      <span class=\\\"text-slate-700\\\">|</span>\\n      <span>SOURCE: NOAA AVIATION WEATHER CENTER</span>\\n    </div>\\n    <p>Built for Student Pilots by <span class=\\\"text-[#38BDF8]\\\">SkyClear Engineering</span> &mdash; Purdue Aerospace Portfolio</p>\\n  </footer>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    }
  }
}
