    web_documents {
      url: "https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF6M2sjKBiwFa3uBveDcDAK5TdEKRA04Zejs_2bW6CgHMY-otc9qh-nLeS9up1naLgKLNRCbaWfxvqoEmZAYu02HO4I6_AHHe--JIdX8I-Y6KBX0rqBQYer-zQz0_mqHBPd"
      title: "vite.dev"
    }
    web_documents {
      url: "https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHJiqa5wiTlXk3sA99wsV0FteoKpZxKSnZYNpPxsPywu9xxBTwds1ngTsOc3x493m4xSBBCyYLCPjFTs44OGdNBMVT3gREvhg2bZpyQHqkxcea_-b1uQGkMpsd9dUZ2wF7ceHvQFC3VaBBjh9KszFtQc3BA"
      title: "generalistprogrammer.com"
    }
    summary: "The \"Cannot set property fetch\" error in a Vite environment typically arises when a script or library attempts to reassign the `fetch` property on the global `window` object, which is often read-only. This can happen due to various reasons, including polyfill conflicts, module resolution issues, or specific library implementations.\n\nHere are the common causes and solutions for this error:\n\n1.  **`window.fetch` is Read-Only**: The most direct cause is that the `fetch` property on the `Window` object is a getter and not directly settable in some browser environments or when specific browser debugging tools are active[1][2][3]. If a script tries to execute `window.fetch = someNewFetchImplementation;`, it will fail with this error.\n\n2.  **Polyfill Conflicts**: When using libraries that rely on Node.js-specific modules (like `buffer` or `process`) in a browser environment, polyfills are often required. Conflicts can arise if these polyfills, or other libraries, incorrectly try to polyfill or redefine `fetch` in a way that clashes with the native implementation or other polyfills[4].\n\n3.  **ESM vs. CommonJS (`node-fetch` specific)**: If you\'re using `node-fetch` and encounter this error after upgrading to Vite, it might be due to a module resolution conflict. Your main application, being ESM, might try to load the ESM version of `node-fetch`, leading to issues. Resolving `node-fetch` to its CommonJS (CJS) version in your `vite.config.js` can sometimes fix this:\n    \n\nSources:\n[1] [github.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE7G-Kd-MQdb5LVqyZHJgjiIEp8jWpxtxxr_3oMaNu5jAPg_993pENpLE5zuZtpGjR9s4t4aRGegdKLW9bpsNKDZ-8xeGAJqELZLdr0keA5laqVuws0jv1d96MDZcRHQqoOgP_m2tnzxLrjEZt2NNHrw1nyV1qYyOZQZDH_atg4)\n[2] [github.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF07WFumB3s9m1BHPGLEdgIa0whwo1uRhXQPtCl5nVMzGLaEib4OiN3iHk-_iBrk2QZZxYRq2K33A2QkAJ8IVp8Pk8lf-qFWXTn1GiUBBIfAvg3IpegwAu903w4Yr3qCET2rt948hbn3HmsFQNEmit8FNCVm9I4YA==)\n[3] [google.dev](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQE3iHleylRqhncOret1NZLKiQiJOY4CJSxgg3gCsN4TBSCKs4phnSEdK6Ls9lGiU3r2pfLYoWsFuJkkVb1yU-o0npD4juFGwwzejqpf4cP4sq548Y42vdpsXnKfpmTsecJ-M9KBeVUMhDGkGj44TdBjyYarfb210ALeTS2n_2oOOwf4PMyePUSJkxkIPb5tU7AZo1z91e6CtVitNc32rtc_0UtnoZwBzNlGMI_lgxAUQCmYSEjAL0U9LIuSGbPscXbIOU1S9BUr)\n[4] [metamask.io](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHL_PNVXS7A-Fz2XcirfQHJ6hyIz3pu5FY7hcqkWvNPHtIAwdZluUCzmqCjFEEoHQPjR03WwQeqZzxV-ll_kDjKn3XgHt-wlpYGI_phHotRmfc3JRQNW_hCpYiLqrMkVWbZxpkUeOrZCeiv4CHZCi_lD3Q-EeP6ewQGJPM5xWgH-II=)\n[5] [stackoverflow.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGhdcDNFGgob6NsTArGS8lwUrdBRbGU70kusm5e9TvDvxH3Nwi8KDsYYxqRJK-YHyVxXP9ZAN00y0fO-pI3rUbxeQw-hr8zyRCfV6vf__fjek22MqwAZRT7CfPyTCURQnrrkaZQ9NX2nA-SDwjZnAl_cpAO6ZQshaCl3VLlCSCqqD_M_Q66AtM68L2x-oOEz_W10CqBlFduAX_LveK3CWm2)\n[6] [stackoverflow.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG2d9vJBpVpLyq1BOL-8hrKJHYMr3JNFSA9t-513p0M3pWsGJmAgpQp75Bupa0LNIdLHne-54MIAI2uyXrdN_q9UtHBh1AliFLkDerLsgDIRLFjuWVNEGHCwZVUU4w_0bNjP3STlGJ07fmTEP0QSgWkWyM7vcw62u3Dqlq0KG1M9mnY)\n[7] [csdn.net](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFQSFqSNXGYEwpYLMj31QgSkvcg0fLywEe6stUXpqTQbeA3awxtCTBpL1WsbuNBRZrJaTkfJOC6o9YfTGFskucEjqRvGlXQvbaHyMxVAan8g5AdTTQcUAHnpLWsBIK94NLIdkcrQEX2SiDNQoxHKmpzXUDBYSvfp3w=)\n[8] [vite.dev](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQF6M2sjKBiwFa3uBveDcDAK5TdEKRA04Zejs_2bW6CgHMY-otc9qh-nLeS9up1naLgKLNRCbaWfxvqoEmZAYu02HO4I6_AHHe--JIdX8I-Y6KBX0rqBQYer-zQz0_mqHBPd)\n[9] [generalistprogrammer.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQHJiqa5wiTlXk3sA99wsV0FteoKpZxKSnZYNpPxsPywu9xxBTwds1ngTsOc3x493m4xSBBCyYLCPjFTs44OGdNBMVT3gREvhg2bZpyQHqkxcea_-b1uQGkMpsd9dUZ2wF7ceHvQFC3VaBBjh9KszFtQc3BA)"
