      url: "https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQFX0jsEFAfouI_bepC4TNd_ey_ax5rhfYI8Qk3wrEUBL6BTSpphfByN6mO9JaMLs5TgVsLf5nl_0Klq33EgOU4GL8ROejXmlzqJhc9JhXScIFNJ5V0tBD8-p8CgAQ1V46BLTw=="
      title: "wheresrhys.co.uk"
    }
    summary: "The error message \"Cannot set property fetch\" \"getter\" \"Window\" indicates an attempt to directly reassign the `fetch` property on the `Window` object in a web browser environment. This action is not permitted because `window.fetch` is a native getter, meaning it is a read-only property designed to retrieve the `fetch` function and cannot be directly overwritten[1].\n\nThis error commonly arises when developers try to:\n*   **Mock `fetch` for testing**: In testing scenarios, developers often need to control the behavior of network requests made by `fetch`.\n*   **Intercept `fetch` requests and responses**: Adding custom logic before or after a `fetch` call, such as for authentication, logging, or modifying requests/responses.\n\n**Solutions and Workarounds:**\n\nSince direct reassignment is not allowed, several strategies can be employed to achieve mocking or interception of `fetch` functionality:\n\n1.  **Using a Proxy Object**: You can wrap the original `window.fetch` with a `Proxy` object. This allows you to intercept calls to `fetch` and inject custom logic without directly reassigning the original getter. The `apply` trap of the `Proxy` object can be used to execute custom code whenever `fetch` is called.[2]\n\n    \n\nSources:\n[1] [google.dev](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQG498ZS0DBH07-y7TQxBQpRpxctLLCNAJBIdi-45Erd2rj7mOK8FsI7XH3OMKQxVhEZYatcI5-hmkqpkS3pMXZUtCrqNh0oR4N7aTM9JTYLpU0qvXZCSGJ2aMZPf7NyGxcLAYBPgpqMjVOy3eWogyvis2sMJTLSw-yvcIsoTY_Vp6W34ArD3ABUr_DQqskhbPRCRBKF9JAckDIFr330nNXTS72hNltA6vshoaFVvf1M)\n[2] [dev.to](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGoGnznYZJA-OTGAzPHxmc8zz7zQXGPXFQFGKsjbzAulIsHmwR86upApz3HgnvOK9VM8sPJt8GDv6yZcSCJvSpt7sFPgnf29faGvBbmJKYiMu33sG8-JMDV5fIPzbmM0aAix7oPWOacYBBhhp9fDU-oZtCwcdmotwVf_3C5DxaK16QuYJ4=)\n[3] [logrocket.com](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/grounding-api-redirect/AUZIYQGdpNCpLATEJSOV6yj1WPrMqA4b9C864tt85-n31LwPhOL8YvRV0h